               <p>- Simmonds deposed that the watchman informed him that there was a man stealing the lead off Mr. Scott's house; that there was some lead thrown down into the street, in <placeName id="t17710410-53-crimeloc282">Grosvenor Place</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17710410-53-crimeloc282" type="placeName" value="Grosvenor Place"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17710410-53-crimeloc282" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17710410-53-off279 t17710410-53-crimeloc282"></join>; that the watchman and he saw the prisoner come out of the area, and they accused him; that then they examined the lead, and found it match the place the lead was cut off from.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17710410-53-person573">
                  Thomas
                   Jones
               <interp inst="t17710410-53-person573" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
